<p>This is my code below</p>  <pre><code>    this.document.namespaces.add("v", "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml");     var cssText =             'v\\: * { behavior:url(#default#VML);  }';     var vmlStyleSheet = this.document.createStyleSheet();     vmlStyleSheet.cssText = cssText;      this.container = this.document.getElementById("mydiv");      var myline = this.document.createElement("v:line");     myline.style.behavior = "url(#default#VML)";     myline.style.display = "inline-block";     myline.setAttribute("from", "50 300");     myline.setAttribute("to", "100 250");      var myfill = this.document.createElement("v:fill");     myfill.setAttribute("on", true);     myfill.setAttribute("color","red");      var mypath = this.document.createElement("v:path");     mypath.setAttribute("textpathok", true);      var mytextpath = this.document.createElement("v:textpath");     mytextpath.setAttribute("on", true);     mytextpath.setAttribute("string", "VML Text");     mytextpath.style.font = "36pt Arial";      myline.appendChild(myfill);     myline.appendChild(mypath);     myline.appendChild(mytextpath);            this.container.appendChild(myline); </code></pre>  <p>This works fine in IE7 and I get a rotated text. Where as the same code is not working in IE8. Any idea what might be wrong?</p>  <p>Thanks</p>